WEBVTT

00:00:01.404 --> 00:00:04.680
Almost 20 years have passed since 9/11.

00:00:06.120 --> 00:00:09.336
It is time to take stock of where we stand

00:00:09.360 --> 00:00:10.800
and stop and think.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:14.096
It is time to ask ourselves,

00:00:14.120 --> 00:00:16.256
have the assumptions and policies

00:00:16.280 --> 00:00:18.576
we developed in the wake
of those tragic events

00:00:18.600 --> 00:00:21.080
truly made us more secure?

00:00:21.880 --> 00:00:26.416
Have they made our societies,
both in Europe and in the United States,

00:00:26.440 --> 00:00:27.640
more resilient?

00:00:28.720 --> 00:00:32.735
I've worked all my life
in the field of security and defense,